::KitKat::

She watched him pull the chair out for her and she blushed slightly. 
She was very impressed with him. She looked at Koj and smiled warmly 
at him. "I'm sorry, but I must ask you to wait here for me. I must 
finish my other business first." SHe turned to DarkMouse, "See that 
they are taken care of properly."
She made a slight curtsie to Koj and Inu an walked out of the 
conference room. She headed back to the other room where Megatron and 
Aracnia and Destructor were.

DarkMouse::
She wasn't at all happy with this. She didn't trust either one of 
them. Her nose told her that something about these two wasn't right. 
But she had her orders. She bowed to Koj and Inu. "Can I get you two 
anything to drink while you wait?"

KitKat::
She walked into the room.  She put a hand on Destructor's shoulder 
and smiled at him. "Everything go OK while I was gone?" She gave him 
a sweet smile and walked over to her chair. She looked at Megatron 
and Aracnia. "So, what do you think? Will that clone due as a 
substitute for battle Megatron?"
